&gt; later on. Think about native Chinese speakers who have difficulty
&gt; distinguishing &#39;l&#39; and &#39;r&#39;. (Contrast between colors, on the other
&gt; hand, is determined physiologically by the sensitivity of each of the
&gt; three different types of cones in the retina to variations in the
